    Bryan
    5.0 out of 5 starsGreat inexpesive but good quality shirt. Fit well
    January 3, 2018
    Verified Purchase
    As a prime member who is used to getting my orders lightning fast, the shipping on this item seemed glacial. But the reviews were great so I went ahead and ordered a medium shirt with the intention of seeing how it fit and ordering more if I liked it. I'm glad I did! I ended up ordering 2 more shirts in different colors for a total of 3!

    FIT:
    I'm 5'11" with a build on the thin side of average and the medium fits me fine. It rides the line right between loose and sloppy, and too tight. In other words, it's a fitted shirt that doesn't make you look like a cheesy body builder from the Jersey shore.

    COLORS:
    I thought the colors matched the pictures pretty spot on. I got black, charcoal and dark blue all of which look pretty good (the charcoal may be just a bit lighter than I expected).

    MATERIAL / QUALITY:
    This shirt definitely feels different than your standard t-shirt. It does have a suede-like feel but after several washes it doesn't feel very strange at all - really just ends up feeling like a nice soft t-shirt that's slightly on the heavier side (probably not ideal for summer but I haven't tried it in hot weather yet.) Quality seems nice - I didn't notice any tears, poor stitching or other abnormalities.
